# Flashcard Component — Design Specification
# FadeJunkie · Lobe Design System
# Created: 2026-03-10

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

## 1. Visual Anatomy

The flashcard is a two-faced card with a 3D flip interaction.
Each card has a FRONT (question) and BACK (answer reveal).
The card lives inside a floating widget panel with navigation chrome.

### Front Face
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ ᴛᴏᴘɪᴄ                tap to flip │  ← badge + hint row
│                                   │
│                                   │
│   What is the technical term      │  ← question text, centered
│   for split ends?                 │
│                                   │
│                                   │
│     A    B    C    D              │  ← letter hints, faded (0.2 opacity)
└─────────────────────────────────┘

- Background: #fff4ea (warm cream)
- Topic badge: top-left, monospace, 9px, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.08em
  Color: #8a7e72 (muted warm gray)
- "Tap to flip" hint: top-right, monospace, 9px, color #b8a99a, opacity 0.7
- Question text: Spectral serif, 16px, weight 400, color #0a0a0a
  Centered vertically and horizontally in the card body
  Line-height: 1.45, max-width: 85% of card width
- Answer letter hints: A B C D in a row at bottom
  Monospace, 11px, weight 600, color #0a0a0a, opacity 0.2
  Spaced evenly, 20px gap between letters
  Serves as a visual hint that options exist on the back

### Back Face
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│                                   │
│  ┌─ A ── Trichoptilosis ───────┐ │  ← correct: white pill, dark text
│  └─────────────────────────────┘ │
│    B    Fragilitas Crinium        │  ← wrong: white text, 0.3 opacity
│    C    Monilethrix               │
│    D    Trichorrhexis Nodosa      │
│                                   │
└─────────────────────────────────┘

- Background: #0a0a0a (near-black)
- Option rows: stacked vertically, 8px gap between rows
  Each row: letter badge + option text, left-aligned
  Padding: 14px horizontal
- Letter badge: monospace, 10px, weight 600
  Width: 20px, height: 20px, border-radius: 4px
  Centered text, inline-flex
- Correct answer row:
  Background: #ffffff, border-radius: 6px, padding: 8px 12px
  Letter badge: background #0a0a0a, color #ffffff
  Text: Spectral, 13px, weight 600, color #0a0a0a
- Wrong answer rows:
  No background (transparent)
  Letter badge: border 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15), color rgba(255,255,255,0.3)
  Text: Spectral, 13px, weight 400, color rgba(255,255,255,0.3)

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

## 2. Card Dimensions & Spacing

- Card width: 100% of widget content area (widget is 320px, so ~288px with padding)
- Card height: 220px (fixed, no overflow scroll)
- Card border-radius: 8px
- Card internal padding: 16px
- No border on either face — the background color shift IS the boundary

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

