| text-hint           | #b8a99a                      | "Tap to flip" hint           |
| text-back-correct   | #0a0a0a                      | Correct answer text (on pill)|
| text-back-wrong     | rgba(255,255,255,0.3)        | Wrong answer text            |
| correct-pill-bg     | #ffffff                      | Correct answer pill           |
| correct-badge-bg    | #0a0a0a                      | Correct answer letter badge  |
| wrong-badge-border  | rgba(255,255,255,0.15)       | Wrong answer badge border    |
